      <title>土耳其禁止卖空，简化回购到STEM市场幻灯片</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/turkey-bans-short-selling-eases-buybacks-to-stem-market-slide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其的资本市场监管机构禁止在所有股票中销售卖空，并放松股票回购规则，以防止市场进一步恶化，该市场在拘留一名著名的反对领导人之后，该国的基准指数损失了17％。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/turkey-bans-short-selling-eases-buybacks-to-stem-market-slide</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 21:31:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
